		</dt>
		<dd class="lead">A $375,000 renovation to the Department of National Defence's deputy minister's office last May came amidst warnings to staff about saving money and impending layoffs. <a href="/news/politics/story/2012/01/16/ottawa-department-defence-office-costs.html" class="more">more <span>&raquo;</span></a></dd>
		
